Gaunt:
     Gaunt stood on the bridge of the Nemisis II with Blackheart, he was one of the troops to raise his hand.
     "Sir," Gaunt said, looking at the view screen, "What is the plan for when we reach Earth? You know Magnus will be there."
 aerosmith60@... wrote:The Tripred council stood up and saluted the general. "You have done our planet a great service. You have finally won the war...but now we have another  mission for you. You must got and bring back our tripred troops and whipe out the Maximals there. Rodimus is our only major threat  left. He also might have the key to opening the matrix of leadership. Go now son of the Pits." Blackheart turned. His black cape swooshed as he turned. The tripred ensignia on the back in gold. "After all of the battles it is over...we have finally taken our rightful place. Now one more mission and ill finally be allowed on the tripred council." He stepped onto his war flagship. The nemesis II (spark destoryer) as he had named it. He stood on the bridge. Looking over the fine group of predacons that he had been asigned to. The same that had helped him win the war. "One last time comrades...lets kick some maximal ass!" The predacon troops raised thier arms with a cheer. He sat down and the ship blasted off into space. The hole in time ripping open. The special tomb laied quiet in the boules of the ship.
